      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：Pending通过payment_received到Confirmed，Confirmed通过start_fulfillment进入Processing，然后dispatched到Shipped，最后received到达Delivered，再连到遥测流。超时和客户取消两个分支我也加上了。",
